      "content": "but it's not just about \"fighting\" anymore. i'm so tired. i see the look in her eyes when she thinks i'm not watching, that exhaustion... it breaks my heart. i just keep thinking, if i wasn't here, she could travel, she could sleep, she could actually live her own life instead of just managing my decline. how is that not a kind thing to do for her?",
